<lb n="0215a27" ed="T"/>主嚕<note place="inline">二十二</note>娑<note place="inline">去<note n="0215016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">引＝聲【明】【乙】</note><app n="0215016"><lem>引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">聲</rdg></app></note>馱野遏貪<app source="0215006" type="＊"><lem>麼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">摩</rdg></app>麼<note place="inline">二十三</note>&CB00576;底也
<lb n="0215a28" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>末他<note n="0215017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">弩＝拏&M062403;【乙】</note><app n="0215017"><lem>弩</lem><rdg resp="【乙】" wit="【？】">拏</rdg></app><note place="inline">鼻引</note><note n="0215018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">婆＝娑【宋】</note><app n="0215018"><lem>婆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">娑</rdg></app><note place="inline">去</note>&CB00085;娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二<note n="0215019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">合＋（引）【三】【乙】</note><note n="0215019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">合＋（引）【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0215019"><lem>合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">合引</rdg></app></note>賀<note place="inline"><note n="0215020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（引）＋二【三】【甲】【乙】＊</note><note n="0215020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（引）＋二【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0215020"><lem>二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">引二</rdg></app>十四</note>吠
