<lb n="0216c02" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0216c0201">若&CB00057;淨<note n="0216037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">油＝洒【三】</note><note n="0216037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">油＝洒【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0216037"><lem>油</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">洒</rdg></app>七<note n="0216038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">遍＋（二七遍）【三】【乙】</note><note n="0216038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遍＋（二七遍）【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0216038"><lem>遍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">遍二七遍</rdg></app>用塗臥所。乞財物等得如
